The "Hours App" is designed to help users record working hours, break hours, and calculate monthly salaries. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data.

1. Information We Collect
Work Hours and Breaks: The app records the work hours and break times you input.
Monthly Salary: The app calculates and stores monthly salary data based on the recorded hours and user-provided salary rate.
Optional Personal Data: If provided, we may store additional information such as employee name and contact details.
2. How We Use Your Information
The data is used solely for the purpose of recording working hours, calculating salary, and sharing work schedules.
We do not share, sell, or disclose your information to third parties.
3. Data Security
All information is stored locally on your device. If you choose to export or share data, it will be your responsibility to secure it.
We implement standard security measures to protect against data loss or misuse.
4. User Control
You can delete or modify your data within the app at any time.
For further assistance, please contact [support@hoursapp.com] (replace with your support email).
5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy periodically. Users will be notified of any significant changes within the app.
6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please reach out to us at [support@hoursapp.com].
